<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="ever-adv">ever <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'evə(r)/    美 /'evər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在 (以往) 任何时候；从来；曾经：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Nothing new ever happens in this little town. 
这个小镇从不发生新鲜事。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Did you ever visit her those days? 
那段时间你去看望过她吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you ever come to London, please let me know. 
你若来伦敦，请告诉我。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It's raining <strong>harder than ever</strong>.
雨下得更大了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is one of the best men I have ever met. 
他是我遇到过的最好的人之一</p></div>

<p>注: ever常用于否定句、一般疑问句以及表示条件和比较的从句，也可与比较级或最高级连用。  </p>
<h4 id="2">2.<strong>究竟；到底：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why ever did you do so? 
你究竟为什么要这么做？</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="ever-after">ever after</h3>
<p>1.<strong>从那时以后一直</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="ever-since">ever since</h3>
<p>1.<strong>自从；从…以来；此后一直：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Their work has influenced other writers ever since. 
他们的作品此后一直影响着后世的作家。</p><footer>外研③ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Project Hope has helped numerous poor students ever since it was founded.
希望工程自创建以来已经帮助了无数的贫困学生。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Attention, coffee lovers! We have for you, the best coffee machine <strong><em>_</em></strong>_invented.  （2006 江西）<br />
A.ever<br />
B.already<br />
C.even<br />
D.nowadays  </li>
<li>I thought she was famous, but none of my friends have <strong><em>_</em></strong>_heard of her.  （2006 广东）<br />
A.even<br />
B.ever<br />
C.just<br />
D.never  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. A  2. B  </p></div>